node.text: #ad Well…it’s time to crown the Ultimate Flamin’ Hot Faceoff champ. After counting all the fan votes, #TeamDoritos has been announced the winner. Just as I expected. Now the whole world knows who reigns supreme when it comes to Flamin’ Hot. Sorry @winnieharlow, but looks like this Harlow is taking home the win. One lucky fan has the chance to win a @doritos watch on July 12th…just follow and comment on @doritos IG post using #FlaminHotFaceOff.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jack Harlow on July 02, 2021. May be an illustration of 1 person and text that says 'CRÊME DE LA TOUR GREME SOLD OUT'.

node.text: Wow. The entire Creme De La Creme Tour is sold out. We used to do shows with 10 people in the crowd. Every night I would struggle through my set, trying to entertain an empty room, telling myself that one day all of my concerts would be packed. Those times are the reason I could never take something like this for granted. Streams and followers are nice…but having real people buy real tickets to come and see you in the flesh is priceless. Thank you for this. More cities and dates to be added…stay tuned. See you soon.
